        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Had that put in,\" he continued, \"and turned the top of the building into a little snuggery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Come up!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Good stuff, those.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Aye, doctor,\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"The fact is-I came here to tell you so!--I know a good deal about everything.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"You've got some limitation to it, I should think.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Ever since Braden was found at the foot of those stairs in Paradise, and I was fetched to him, I've interested myself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Oh!\" he said after a pause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Dear me!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Lots!\" answered Bryce.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"I came to tell you-on seeing that Glassdale had been with you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Because-I was with Glassdale this morning.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "But Bryce saw that his cool, almost indifferent manner was changing-he was beginning, under the surface, to get anxious.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"When I left Glassdale-at noon,\" continued Bryce, \"I'd no idea-and I don't think he had-that he was coming to see you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "But all that Glassdale knows is nothing-to what I know.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "He threw it away, took a fresh one from the box, and slowly struck a match and lighted it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"What might you know, now?\" he asked after another pause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000032_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000032_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "I went back-to the time when Braden was married.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "He got to know-got into close touch with a Barthorpe man who, about the time of Brake's marriage, left Barthorpe end settled in London.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000034_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000034_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "I know what happened-he used to let them have money for short financial transactions-to be refunded within a very brief space.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000034_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000034_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "He had to stand the racket.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000034_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000034_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "He stood it-to the tune of ten years' penal servitude.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"The name of the particular one was Wraye-Falkiner Wraye,\" replied Bryce promptly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Of the other-the man of lesser importance-Flood.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"I will!--it's deeply interesting.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "mr Falkiner Wraye, after cheating and deceiving Brake, and leaving him to pay the penalty of his over trustfulness, cleared out of England and carried his money making talents to foreign parts.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000041_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000041_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "What is it?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"We've not come to that,\" retorted Bryce.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"You're a bit mistaken.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000042_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000042_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Look here!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000042_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000042_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Come, now!--whose?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"That's a fact?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Then who had?\" demanded Bryce.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "He was evidently thinking deeply, and Bryce made no attempt to disturb him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_133471_000046_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/133471/476_133471_000046_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Some minutes went by before Folliot took the cigar from his lips and leaning against the chimneypiece looked fixedly at his visitor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
