        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Get down into the bottom and pull a sack over you, and do not get up until the car stops.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Like an automaton john put down his brushes, and walked slowly to the gate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000049_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000049_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Now it was going fast, now faster, now it rocked and swayed as it gathered speed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"Get out,\" said a voice.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000054_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000054_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Where could he go?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000056_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000056_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "At the foot there was a smooth stretch of green sward.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000059_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000059_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"But, I do not understand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000067_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000067_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "They discovered your escape,\" he said. \"Get in.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000070_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000070_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "He clicked over a lever and with a roar the big three bladed tractor screw spun.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000072_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000072_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Up, up, they climbed in one long sweeping ascent, passing through drifting clouds till the machine soared like a bird above the blue sea.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000073_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000073_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "john Lexman looked down.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000074_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000074_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Talking was impossible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000075_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000075_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Kara was evidently a skilful pilot.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000075_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000075_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "From time to time he consulted the compass on the board before him, and changed his course ever so slightly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000076_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000076_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "john Lexman read:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000077_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000077_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"If you cannot swim there is a life belt under your seat.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000082_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000082_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "A white steam yacht, long and narrow of beam, was steaming slowly westward.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000082_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000082_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "He could see the feathery wake in her rear, and as the aeroplane fell he had time to observe that a boat had been put off.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000082_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000082_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Then with a jerk the monoplane flattened out and came like a skimming bird to the surface of the water; her engines stopped.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000083_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000083_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "\"We ought to be able to keep afloat for ten minutes,\" said Kara, \"and by that time they will pick us up.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000085_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000085_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "In less than five minutes the boat had come alongside, manned, as Lexman gathered from a glimpse of the crew, by Greeks.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-476_134312_000085_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/476/134312/476_134312_000085_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-476",
        "content": "Kara was by his side.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]